Package: teatime-unity
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, gir1.2-unity-5.0, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-notify-0.7, gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0, pulseaudio-utils, sound-theme-freedesktop
Description: Simple egg timer application for the Unity Desktop
 A simple egg-timer type application to time your teas. 
 Rings an alarm and displays an desktop notification, when the tea is ready. 
 Supports saving several pre-set timers.
